         <div class="news_title">
          <a href="newsDetail_forward_1523669">装甲兵学院由原总参谋部军训和兵种部转隶陆军</a>
         </div> 
         <div class="__BAIDUNEWS__infos"> 
          <span class="__BAIDUNEWS__tm">2016-09-03 15:37</span> 
          <span class="__BAIDUNEWS__source">来源：<a href="http://www.thepaper.cn">澎湃新闻</a></span> 
          <span class="__BAIDUNEWS__author">澎湃新闻记者 岳怀让</span> 
          <div class="__BAIDUNEWS__shares"> 
           <div class="bdsharebuttonbox" data-tag="__BAIDUNEWS__share_1"> 
            <a class="__BAIDUNEWS__bds bds_more" data-cmd="more"><i class="iishare"></i>分享</a> 
            <a href="#" class="__BAIDUNEWS__bds bds_tsina" data-cmd="tsina" title="分享到新浪微博"></a> 
            <a href="#" class="__BAIDUNEWS__bds bds_renren" data-cmd="renren" title="分享到人人网"></a> 
            <a href="#" class="__BAIDUNEWS__bds bds_douban" data-cmd="douban" title="分享到豆瓣网"></a> 
            <a href="#" class="__BAIDUNEWS__bds bds_tqq" data-cmd="tqq" title="分享到腾讯微博"></a> 
            <a href="#" class="__BAIDUNEWS__bds bds_weixin" data-cmd="weixin" title="分享到微信"></a> 
